@@TJvCustomPreviewControl
Summary
  Control that can display a print preview window, simulating how a document would look if it was
  sent to a printing device.
Description
  TJvCustomPreviewControl is the base class for controls that can display a print preview, zoom and
  scroll between pages. TJvCustomPreviewControl implements the basic behavior and descendant classes
  expose and extend it. Don't put a TJvCustomPreviewControl on a form. Instead, use one of the
  derived classes that publishes many of the properties of TJvCustomPreviewControl, like
  TJvPreviewControl.

