@@TJvCustomPreviewControl.Add
Summary
  Adds a new page to the preview.
Description
  Call Add to add a new page to the preview. Add calls OnAddPage which in turn must be handled so it
  draws the page content on the new page.

  You don't need to call Add if you are using a renderer to create the preview. Only use Add when
  creating custom previews.
Return value
  True if the page was added, false otherwise.
See Also
  TJvCustomPreviewControl.OnAddPage

